dc_title_s: Map of part of the north shore of Lake Huron compiled from map issued by the Dept. of Crown Lands and from rangers' maps.
dc_description_s: Shows the Canadian Pacific Railway and Sault Ste. Marie branch of the CPR. 1 map: col.; 43 x 58 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
